<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Email Verification Error</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            color: #3e3e3e;
        }

        .email-container {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            width: 600px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .header {
            text-align: center;
            background-color: #f44336;
            padding: 10px;
            color: white;
            border-radius: 10px 10px 0 0;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .retry-button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #f44336;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }

        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #777;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Email Verification Error</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Dear User,</p>
            <p>We encountered an issue while verifying your email address. Please try again by clicking the button
                below:</p>
            <p style="text-align: center;">
                <a href="#" class="retry-button">Retry Verification</a>
            </p>
            <p>If the problem continues, feel free to reach out to our support team for further assistance.</p>
            <p>We apologize for any inconvenience caused.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; 2024 Your Company. All Rights Reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>